channel.title: Port Forwarding problem
channel.description:
I'm trying to learn to run my own server and i have a problem when i try to go to my router settings. I got my ip and when i type it in my browser it redirects me to www.ask.com and my ip is in the search browser and it says "this search cannot be completed please try a broader search". Now i typed my ip in my browser..i have no idea why it sends me to www.ask.com, please someone if you can help me?
I use windows xp,internet explorer,arris is my router(model is tm502b).
